query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS performanceSnapshots (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  userId INT NOT NULL,
  snapshotType ENUM('before_fix', 'after_fix') NOT NULL,
  fixType VARCHAR(100),
  bootTimeSeconds INT,
  cpuUsagePercent INT,
  memoryUsagePercent INT,
  diskUsagePercent INT,
  startupProgramsCount INT,
  outdatedDriversCount INT,
  securityIssuesCount INT,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)
